河马、羊等动物混养的尝试，“不过此前并未引发如此大的舆论关注。” 她还告诉潮新闻记者，项目自开展以来，动物园方面都有进行长期的观察和记录，也有严格的项目流程。“根据我们记录的影像资料来看，两种动物之间的互动还是非常友好的，后续我们可能也会陆续向公众公布一些（画面）。” 针对社群丰容项目后续的开展，该名工作人员表示，“这个项目既然开展了我们后面还是会进行下去，不能半途而废。”动物园内猩猩“欺负”卡皮巴拉？工作人员：“混养”属于社群丰容项目"},"attached_info":"CkEIs9/ggqDljpYEEAMaCTExMjc0Nzk3MSCMx+27BjAAON4BQBpyCjg4NTc1NjI3MTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"46 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-07034f2a57a1ba2116e32c4af1778c3c_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1736238155.18618","card_id":"Q_759937461","target":{"id":759937461,"title":"为什么刀郎演唱会爆满，座无虚席？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/759937461","type":"question","created":1728207167,"answer_count":100,"follower_count":182,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[317,12115],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"请说出其中的缘由，喜欢刀郎的都是几零后的人呢"},"attached_info":"CkAIs9/ggqDljpYEEAMaCTExMDk3NDMwNyC/som4BjAAOLYBQBtyCTc1OTkzNzQ2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"46 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-695f2ffc5db554bac9bc04b36221cf0b_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1736238155.19805","card_id":"Q_649418282","target":{"id":649418282,"title":"按科研实力来说，港八校相当于内地什么水平的院校？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/649418282","type":"question","created":1710950572,"answer_count":20,"follower_count":69,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2819,5308,7575,44626,45616],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Is9/ggqDljpYEEAMaCTEwNjU5MjgyMSCskeyvBjAAOEVAHHIJNjQ5NDE4MjgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"46 